the same trend line.\nThis could result from similar formation processes, possibly hierarchical\ncluster assembly. We argue that NGC 6231 has expanded from its initial size but\nthat it remains gravitationally bound.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Oct 2017 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
