\nand thermal plateau emission produced by the ejection of the outer envelope of\nblue supergiant and Wolf-Rayet progenitors in otherwise failed supernovae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Oct 2017 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Feb 2018 04:10:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
