e\ntransient toroidal configuration to form, and discuss implication of our\nfindings on future GW observation targeting rapidly rotating NSs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Oct 2017 04:43:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-08"}
